2026-06-19 10:52:18,894 DEBUG Tool call: retrieve_information({'prompt': 'Extract the key information about how US Steel has addressed the planned merger with Nippon Steel and its effect on its business operations. Please look at the following sources and provide a comprehensive summary:\n\n1. Wikipedia article: {{wikipedia_nippon_us_steel}}\n2. US Steel 2024 10-K Annual Report (risk factors and management discussion): {{us_steel_10k_2024}}\n3. US Steel 8-K filing about Nippon Steel block (January 3, 2025): {{us_steel_8k_nippon_block}}\n4. US Steel DEFA14A filing (March 26, 2025): {{us_steel_defa14a_20250326}}\n5. US Steel DEFA14A filing (March 25, 2025): {{us_steel_defa14a_20250325}}\n6. US Steel DEFA14A filing (February 2, 2024): {{us_steel_defa14a_20240202}}\n7. US Steel 8-K filing (May 21, 2024): {{us_steel_8k_20240521}}\n\nPlease include:\n- Key dates and timeline\n- How US Steel has addressed the merger in official communications\n- What US Steel has said about the effect of the merger on its business operations\n- Legal actions taken\n- Stockholder votes and approvals\n- Any plans or commitments related to the merger\n- How the uncertainty of the merger has affected operations'})
2026-06-19 10:52:45,641 DEBUG Tool result: ToolCallRecord(
    tool_call=ToolCall(
        id='call_00_tYaxIszei8sRhheXraYP2224',
